screen_name: So this morning, I found out I've tested positive for Covid-19. This shocked me, as my symptoms were very mild compared with the patients I've cared for. But thanks to Donald Trump, I'll be fighting fit in no time. Stay safe everyone. #upyourscovid19 https://t.co/nZHpDb5a0T
